graph.name: The Trump Network
graph.subtitle: Mapping the network of power relations around Donald Trump
graph.description:
This map is created using the Buzzfeed research data and LittleSis.org profiles. This work is not a complete map of Trump’s world, both organizations invite you to contribute additional data, the map will be updated accordingly.

Read the analysis of The Trump Network
https://medium.com/graph-commons/the-trump-network-8610c92035fb
